{"lemma":"فَرِهَةٍ","slug":"فَرِهَةٍ","root":"ف.ر.ه","root_slug":"ف-ر-ه","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ر-ه","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33314","n33315","n33746","","n33749","n42167"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%87%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of وَفَرَ (wafara) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"singulative of فِرّ (firr, “quail”)","tags":["form-of","singulative"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33314","headword_ar":"فُرَّةٌ","root":"fr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ufur~apN","text_ar":"اُفُرَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afur~apN","text_ar":"اَفُرَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beginning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the heat: (T, S, M, O, K:) or they signify, (T, S, M,) or signify also, (O, K,) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: (S, M, O, K:) but [Az says,] the second and third are in my opinion from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afara","text_ar":"اَفَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"being the first radical letter: and Ks states that some change the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E","text_ar":"ع"},{"kind":"text","text":", saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eufur~ap","text_ar":"عُفُرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eafur~ap","text_ar":"عَفُرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ar~Kmino fulaAnK","text_ar":"شَرٍّمِنْ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA zaAla fulaAnN fiY A^ufur~apK","text_ar":"مَا زَالَ فُلَانٌ فِى اُفُرَّةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a saying mentioned by Lth, (T, TA,) meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one ceased not to be"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a vehement state of evil"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mischief"},{"kind":"text","text":"[proceeding"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Confusion and difficulty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqaEa Alqawomu fiY fur~apK","text_ar":"وَقَعَ القَوْمُ فِى فُرَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ufur~apK","text_ar":"اُفُرَّةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afur~apK","text_ar":"اَفُرَّةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, fell into confusion and difficulty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b3-  See also the next preceding paragraph, in three places."}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n33315","headword_ar":"فِرَّةٌ","root":"fr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A smiling:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a manner of smiling:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_n~ahA laHasanapu Alfir~api","text_ar":"اـنَّها لَحَسَنَةُ الفِرَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily she is beautiful in respect of the manner of smiling"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n33746","headword_ar":"فَرُهَ","root":"frh","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraAhapN","text_ar":"فَرَاهَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraAhiyapN","text_ar":"فَرَاهِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) [and app. also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furuwhapN","text_ar":"فُرُوهَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", expl. below as a simple subst.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, skilled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skilful."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faruha","text_ar":"فَرُهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraha","text_ar":"فَرَهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. of each"},{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n. app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furuwhapN","text_ar":"فُرُوهَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraAhapN","text_ar":"فَرَاهَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraAhiyapN","text_ar":"فَرَاهِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", expl. below as simple substs.,] said of a horse or similar beast, &c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, brisk, lively, sprightly, active, agile,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b3-  [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faruha","text_ar":"فَرُهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraAhapN","text_ar":"فَرَاهَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (of which see an explanation below,) probably signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, beautiful, comely, pretty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabuHa","text_ar":"صَبُحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaAHapN","text_ar":"صَبَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariha","text_ar":"فَرِهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farahN","text_ar":"فَرَهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He exulted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rejoiced above measure;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he exulted greatly, and behaved insolently and unthankfully,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ungratefully:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h","text_ar":"ه"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this verb, accord. to Fr, is substituted for the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H","text_ar":"ح"},{"kind":"text","text":"in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHa","text_ar":"فَرِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which has this meaning. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TK"]},{"entry_id":"n33749","headword_ar":"فَرِهٌ","root":"frh","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariha","text_ar":"فَرِهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Exulting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rejoicing above measure;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. In the Kur xxvi. 149, some read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farihiyna","text_ar":"فَرِهِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariha","text_ar":"فَرِهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifying as expl. above: others reading"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faArihiyna","text_ar":"فَارِهِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faruha","text_ar":"فَرُهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) ―         -b2-  but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farihN","text_ar":"فَرِهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faArihN","text_ar":"فَارِهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as an epithet applied to a youth, or young man, or male slave; and thus the reading of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farihiyna","text_ar":"فَرِهِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the Kur has been expl. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Possessing skill."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n42167","headword_ar":"فِرَةٌ","root":"wfr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wufuwrN","text_ar":"وُفُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}